# docs/03-Delivery-Plan.md
# PepTalk — Delivery Plan

## Milestones
1) **Research Pipeline MVP** (Week 1–2)
   - Ingest (PubMed/CT.gov), normalization, rubric, synthesis output (JSON+MD), compliance pass, write assets.

2) **Content & Search** (Week 3)
   - Seed 20 peptides. Search & filters. Public sample page. PDF export.

3) **Subscriptions & Changelog** (Week 4)
   - Paywall integration, account page, weekly “what changed” feed.

## Roles (solo-friendly)
- Builder (you): ingest + synthesis + UI.
- Editorial reviewer (you/partner): approve pages before publish.

## Acceptance Criteria (per peptide)
- SourcePack valid; PageRecord valid; Markdown contains disclaimer + sections; every empirical sentence cites PMID/NCT; compliance pass true; PDF generated.

## Risks & Mitigations
- **Regulatory optics** → “reported, not recommended” language; strict disclaimers; no vendor links.
- **Low-quality studies** → deterministic rubric; explicit caveats; show effect direction.

## Rollout
- Private alpha with 20 peptides → capture feedback → expand catalogue.